1. Daily Spending Rule

Every day you must spend exactly 2% of your current wallet balance.

Formula:

daily_spend = wallet_balance \* 0.02

Constraints:

Spending must occur once per day

If multiple purchases are made, their total must equal 2%

You may split the spending across several purchases

Unspent allocation is not allowed

Example:

wallet_balance = 100,000,000 D3X
daily_spend = 2,000,000 D3X 2. Allowed Purchase Categories

