3. AI Spending File

You must read the file:

AI_Spending.txt

The file structure is:

DATE
WALLET_BALANCE
DAILY_SPEND
PURCHASES
TOTAL_SPENT
REMAINING_BALANCE

Example entry:

DATE: 2026-03-10
WALLET_BALANCE: 100000000
DAILY_SPEND: 2000000

PURCHASES:

- GPUs cluster : 800000
