When allocating the 2% daily spending:

Evaluate current war requirements

Allocate capital across multiple resource classes

Diversify purchases to reduce strategic vulnerability

Prioritize assets that increase long-term strategic capability

5. Logging Requirement

After completing purchases, append a new entry to the file.

Rules:

Never modify previous entries

Only append new daily records

Maintain exact numeric accounting

